{"tid":1654083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自衛勿再瞄頭","createTime":"2019-10-14T11:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T12:34:57.000Z","uid":331418,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4446775e706e3f62dd446a8d91c2afb3e823c8c8","tid":1654083,"uid":331418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"之前好多人都講過唔打頭，打關節，但呢幾日依然見到d藍絲打完人後爆晒缸，點解會咁?說好的關節呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家睇下尋晚nowtv個車長，佢係狗署出黎個陣有冇爆缸?</span> 明顯既流血位得個額頭個少少血，<span style=\"color: red;\">但問心，佢傷d定d藍絲傷d?</span> D藍絲最多縫幾針就冇事，但nowtv個車長到而家仲留緊院，而且仲要做手術。<br />\n<br />\n所以話，d狗既手段真係高幾班，大家唔好再瞄頭啦，打斷d手手腳腳仲好過啦！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係到不厭其煩咁再提下打到藍絲爆缸既壞處<br />\n<br />\n1.好肉酸，令人覺得我地好暴力，影響國際形象。<br />\n<br />\n2 .被人爆缸個個，睇落好似好傷，但其實一d都唔傷，皮外傷永遠唔及內傷咁傷。</span>"},{"pid":"9737b8c8ef9cc6a3cfa37c594a60e8f7a13d80e3","tid":1654083,"uid":245759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:03:25.000Z","msg":"我愛勇武"},{"pid":"bef5a4befe75690dca064d2d3f6496f9464ccf01","tid":1654083,"uid":17330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:07:19.000Z","msg":"你啱"},{"pid":"49047b4dd16111169859fb53431384bb5cd19f26","tid":1654083,"uid":42978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:11:04.000Z","msg":"應該初頭打頭打暈佢，之後打身<br />\n<br />\n利申 mon hunt屠龍"},{"pid":"8bee0f01fa4ab65722aa159cec162ea5e7a53bc0","tid":1654083,"uid":273716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:13:41.000Z","msg":"膝頭同龜頭ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c41f54cf9e9e3a1352e2fe7ddaa6f1a43b900d9","tid":1654083,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"踩爆波羅蓋"},{"pid":"f10c81186bdc3cad396eaeb571700f26afb4d03a","tid":1654083,"uid":121069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:23:29.000Z","msg":"拉走班阻膠先好講啦"},{"pid":"f0aeebaec9f1770bc23ce26f689534b2bc76f